<title>Kıeli Rýh, Seniń qasyńda</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
.F#              C#                B
 Kıeli Rýh, Seniń qasyńda, máńgi bolǵym keledi
.G#m         C#7
 Qushaǵyńa alshy.
.      F#         C#             B         G#m     C#7
 Kıeli Rýh, názik júzińdi, júregimmen sezem, toltyrshy.

[C1]
.       B    G#m   C#7
   Kıeli Rýh, Kıeli Rýh !
.       B    G#m   C#7
   Kıeli Rýh, Kıeli Rýh !
.           F#/C#           D#m
   Óz ómirimdi, Saǵan baǵyshtaımyn.
.              B          G#m      C#7
   Birtutas bolǵym keledi, Senimen Iem !
.            F#/C#        D#m
   Rızamyn Saǵan, jetele meni.
.              B          G#m   C#7   F#
   Saǵan teńdes eshkim joq, súıemin Seni !

[B1]
.  F#    B            D#m        G#m        F#
    Shyn júrekten, rahmetimdi, Saǵan ǵana aıtamyn!
.    B              D#m       G#m        C#7
   Suraımyn Seni, jeteleshi, Ákemniń taǵyna!</lyrics>
<key>F#</key>
</song>